      "content": "oh wow okay i do have some xanax in my bag from my doctor. do u think i should take the 5mg now? i'm really worried about the chest thing though, it's kind of making me feel lightheaded too. if i take the pill will the chest pain go away? it's just a bit scary because i'm all alone here.",
